draw_text(info1_x, info1_y, "Katyusha is a Soviet folk-based song and military\nmarch. Created in 1938, this song by Matvey Blanter\ngained fame during World War II as a patriotic\nsong which inspired the comrades to serve and defend\ntheir motherland. The song is about a Russian woman\ncalled Katyusha. Standing on a steep riverbank, she\nsends her song to her lover, a soldier serving far away\nwho will protect the Motherlandand its people.");